      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sound E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This example has been properly sorted with the critical rear subframe reinforcement and a recent valve shim adjustment. The 6-speed manual gearbox provides precise engagement, paired with a limited-slip differential that maintains excellent lateral grip. The suspension geometry is tight, benefiting from refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers, while the braking system features upgraded stainless steel lines for improved hydraulic feedback. A true driver\u2019s car with a healthy powertrain and rigid chassis dynamics.",
