      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle strikes the perfect balance between luxury and everyday utility. The exterior features a deep metallic finish that still catches the light beautifully; while there are a few minor stone chips on the front bumper consistent with careful highway use, the body remains straight and free of major blemishes. Step inside to find a meticulously kept cabin featuring charcoal leather upholstery that remains supple and supportive, showing only light natural creasing on the driver\u2019s side. Every electronic component, from the intuitive touchscreen interface to the dual-zone climate control, operates exactly as it should. Under the hood, the engine is clean and responsive, benefiting from a full service history at authorized centers. The transmission shifts seamlessly, and the ride is quiet and composed, thanks to a well-maintained suspension and tires with plenty of life left. This is a dependable, high-quality car that has been treated with respect by its previous owner and is ready for its next chapter.",
